(394, 1, '2014-04-29 06:44:28', '2014-04-29 05:44:28', 'The Hardt Foundation facilities (main house, orangery, greenhouse, garden and park) are available upon request for events (conferences, colloquia, seminars, concerts and other events) on various topics in which classical Antiquity has a prominent, but not exclusive, place.\r\n\r\nEvents organised by private individuals are also welcome. The orangery has been renovated and transformed in order to host such events.\r\n\r\nFor events over several days, accommodation of guests is possible according to availability, before or after the annual closure from December to January as well as before or after the Entretiens sur l’Antiquité classique that take place during the last week of August.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Rental-of-facilities-price-list.pdf">Rental of facilities price list</a>', 'Rental of the facilities', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'location-des-espaces_en', '', '', '2014-05-14 16:16:01', '2014-05-14 15:16:01', '', 384, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=394', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(395, 1, '2014-04-29 06:44:41', '2014-04-29 05:44:41', '<strong>Secrétaire scientifique</strong>\r\nEmail : <a href="mailto:admin@fondationhardt.ch">admin@fondationhardt.ch</a>\r\nTéléphone : + 41 (0) 22 736 31 04\r\nFax : + 41 (0) 22 736 31 06\r\n\r\n<strong>Secrétaire administrative</strong>\r\nMme Patricia Burdet\r\nEmail : <a href="mailto:patricia.burdet@fondationhardt.ch">patricia.burdet@fondationhardt.ch</a>\r\nTéléphone : + 41 (0) 22 736 31 04\r\nFax : + 41 (0) 22 736 31 06\r\n\r\n<strong>Bibliothécaire</strong>\r\nMme Pascale Derron\r\nEmail : <a href="mailto:biblio@fondationhardt.ch">biblio@fondationhardt.ch</a>\r\nTéléphone : +41 (0) 22 736 31 24\r\n\r\n<strong>Directeur</strong>\r\nM. Pierre Ducrey\r\nEmail : <a href="mailto:Pierre.Ducrey@unil.ch">Pierre.Ducrey@unil.ch</a>', 'Contact', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'contact_en', '', '', '2014-05-14 21:27:21', '2014-05-14 20:27:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=395', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(396, 1, '2014-04-29 06:44:49', '2014-04-29 05:44:49', 'The Entretiens sur l’Antiquité classique.\r\n\r\n“<em>Each year, at the Foundation’s home in Vandœuvres, the ‘Entretiens sur l’Antiquité Classique’ will be held, during which specialists from all over the world will speak about a chosen field, and in the course of further discussions will engage in enriching exchange of views</em>.” These were Baron Kurd von Hardt’s own words in the introduction to the first volume of the Entretiens, published in 1954 under the title La notion du divin depuis Homère jusqu’à Platon.\r\n\r\nSince 1952, 60 Entretiens have taken place on a variety of topics. The 60 volumes of the proceedings and following discussions offer an overview of classical culture as approached by over 200 scholars.', 'Entretiens', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'entretiens_en', '', '', '2014-05-07 10:42:47', '2014-05-07 09:42:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=396', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(397, 1, '2014-04-29 06:44:58', '2014-04-29 05:44:58', '<strong>LX.</strong> <em>Les jardins dans l’Antiquité,</em> 2013 (2014)\r\n\r\n<strong>LIX.</strong> <em>Les Grecs héritiers des Romains,</em> 2012 (2013)\r\n\r\n<strong>LVIII.</strong> <em>L’organisation des spectacles dans le monde romain,</em> 2011 (2012)\r\n\r\n<strong>LVII.</strong> <em>Entre Orient et Occident : la philosophie et la science gréco-romaines dans le monde arabe,</em> 2010 (2011)\r\n\r\n<strong>LVI.</strong> <em>Démocratie athénienne – démocratie moderne : tradition et influences,</em> 2009 (2010)\r\n\r\n<strong>LV.</strong> <em>Eschyle à l’aube du théâtre occidental,</em> 2008 (2009)\r\n\r\n<strong>LIV.</strong> <em>Sécurité collective et ordre public dans les sociétés anciennes,</em> 2007 (2008)\r\n\r\n<strong>LIII.</strong> <em>Rites et croyances dans les religions du monde romain,</em> 2006 (2007)\r\n\r\n<strong>LII.</strong> <em>La poésie épique grecque : métamorphoses d’un genre littéraire,</em> 2005 (2006)\r\n\r\n<strong>LI.</strong> <em>L’apologétique chrétienne gréco-latine à l’époque prénicénienne,</em> 2004 (2005)\r\n\r\n<strong>L.</strong> <em>Sénèque le tragique,</em> 2003 (2004)\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Liste-complete-des-Entretiens.pdf" target="_blank">Complete list of the Entretiens</a>\r\n<a href="http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Liste-detaillee-des-volumes-publies.pdf" target="_blank">Detailed list of published volumes</a>', 'The Entretiens collection', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'la-serie-des-entretiens_en', '', '', '2014-05-14 15:15:01', '2014-05-14 14:15:01', '', 396, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=397', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(398, 1, '2014-04-29 06:45:06', '2014-04-29 05:45:06', 'The 61st Entretiens sur l''Antiquité classique will take place from August 25 to 29, 2014 on the topic\r\n\r\n“<strong>Cosmologies et cosmogonies dans la littérature antique – Cosmologies and Cosmogonies in Ancient Literature</strong>.”\r\n\r\nThese Entretiens are under the direction of Therese Fuhrer and Michael Erler.\r\n\r\nProgramme of the 61st  Entretiens sur l''Antiquité classique.\r\n\r\nList of previous Entretiens', 'Upcoming Entretiens ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'prochains-entretiens_en', '', '', '2014-05-06 13:57:35', '2014-05-06 12:57:35', '', 396, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=398', 0, 'page', '', 0),
