(669, 1, '2014-05-06 14:11:04', '2014-05-06 13:11:04', 'The Hardt Foundation facilities (main house, orangery, greenhouse, garden and park) are available upon request for events (conferences, colloquia, seminars, concerts and other events) on various topics in which classical Antiquity has a prominent, but not exclusive, place.\r\n\r\nEvents organised by private individuals are also welcome. The orangery has been renovated and transformed in order to host such events.\r\n\r\nFor events over several days, accommodation of guests is possible according to availability, before or after the annual closure from December to January as well as before or after the Entretiens sur l’Antiquité classique that take place during the last week of August.', 'Conferences and events', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-06 14:11:04', '2014-05-06 13:11:04', '', 384, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?p=669', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
