(445, 1, '2014-04-29 06:49:01', '2014-04-29 05:49:01', '<strong>5 May 1888 </strong>\r\nTitle bestowed on Richard Hardt, grandfather of Kurd, descendant of a dynasty of textile producers. The family receives the barony of Wonsowo, named after its estate in East Prussia (present-day Poland).\r\n\r\n<strong>7 December 1889</strong>\r\nBirth of Kurd von Hardt in Cassel (Germany), son of Friedrich Wilhelm and Anna Elisabeth, née Mumm von Schwarzenstein, from Frankfurt, 5th child of the couple, who will have 6.\r\n\r\n<strong>1911-1913   </strong>\r\nTravels in South America\r\n\r\n<strong>1914-1915  </strong>\r\nHospitalised in a clinic in Davos to treat his tuberculosis.\r\n\r\n<strong>1915-1918</strong>\r\nGerman diplomatic service. His tuberculosis recurs.\r\n\r\n<strong>1919-1938</strong>\r\nSettles in Tuscany (Italy) and Ticino (Switzerland).\r\n\r\n<strong>1938-1948</strong>\r\nResides in Ticino.\r\n\r\n<strong>1948 </strong>\r\nRents the des Gouttes estate in Vandœuvres.\r\n\r\n<strong>1949 </strong>\r\nCreates the Foundation.\r\n\r\n<strong>1950 </strong>\r\nPurchases the estate.\r\n\r\n<strong>1958  </strong>\r\nDeath of Baron. Burial in the park of the Foundation.', 'Baron Kurd von Hardt (1889-1958)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'le-baron-kurd-von-hardt-1889-1958_en', '', '', '2014-05-05 16:23:00', '2014-05-05 15:23:00', '', 439, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=445', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(446, 1, '2014-04-29 06:49:08', '2014-04-29 05:49:08', 'The Hardt Foundation is located on a wooded estate that includes several buildings: the main house, where guests are accommodated, the library, the orangery and the greenhouse. The buildings date to the 19th century, and were recently renovated and modernised.\r\n\r\nThe estate includes a large natural lawn adorned with a pool, a wooded section with a trail for walking or running and a closed garden with fruit trees.\r\n\r\nThe estate of the Hardt Foundation is listed on the Genevan registry of protected buildings.', 'The estate', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'le-domaine_en', '', '', '2014-05-05 16:19:51', '2014-05-05 15:19:51', '', 439, 'http://localhost/www_fondationHardt/?page_id=446', 0, 'page', '', 0),
